          "description": "I had my tooth re-crowned today at Hudson Dental in NYC, and I had such an amazing experience with Dr. G and her entire team. I was extremely nervous about getting my crown replaced, but everyone was so professional, patient, and reassuring throughout the whole process.\n\nThey were able to remove my old crown and create my new crown in less than a week, which was incredibly impressive. Dr. G was so friendly and took the time to guide me through every step, making me feel comfortable and informed the entire time.\n\nThe atmosphere was so calming that I honestly felt like I was in a yoga class instead of a dental office! I\u2019m so grateful for their care, kindness, and expertise. Highly recommend Hudson Dental to anyone looking for a compassionate and professional dental team.",
