          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLh1TqOs2izO41dJ4bTftNA7V1LNYm_tSiZiTwCIcgQcjf0Xw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Came here from a referral from a coworker after a horrible visit to another dental office. (Horrible is an understatement)\nWas nice from the moment I walked thru the doors by a welcoming staff. Not by a generic, \u201chello, how are you?\u201d. Staff was kind, soft spoken and especially patient.\nI also wanted a 2nd opinion from another dentist, after the horrible 30sec exam I had at the last office.\nDr. Ellie (hope I spelled her name correctly) who examined me was so nice, so professional and she introduced herself! She took the time to completely explain everything to me, from diagnosis, the x-rays to future work that needed to be done, step by step. I\u2019m not really an educated person, but she took the time to make sure I understood the situation with my teeth, instead of throwing big medical/dental terminology at me.\nAlthough I left the place with bad news, (do NOT neglect your teeth ppl!!!) I left very happy and content, fully confident that I/my teeth was in good hands. Thank you Hudson Dental!",
